oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 20th Joe Val Bluegrass Festival
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bluegrass music; Music festivals; Skaggs, Ricky; Kentucky Thunder (Musical group); Gibson Brothers (Bluegrass group); Williams, Robin, 1951-2014; King Wilkie (Musical group); Hunger Mountain Boys; Woodcuts (prints); Musical instruments; Mandolin;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (black and red on white) announcing the 20th Joe Val Bluegrass Festival featuring Ricky Skaggs and Kentucky Thunder, Illrad Tyme Out, the Gibson Brothers, Special Consensus, Robin and Linda Williams, David Davis and the Warrior River Boys, King Wilkie, the Kruger Brothers, Bluegrass Gospel Project, Gaudreau and Klein, the Hunger Mountain Boys, Mike Burns and North Country, Freewheelin', Flynn Cohen and the Chagrin River Band, Back Eddy Bluegrass, the Reunion Band, Big Apple'achia, Old Time Bluegrass Singers, Buddy Merriam and Back Roads, and Erica Brown at the Sheraton Framingham on February 18-20. Poster features a woodcut of a mandolin.
